data.description: Zoned B-2 and R-2 see attachment for usage. This is a rare investment opportunity with 10.45 beautifully wooded acres waiting to be enjoyed and/or developed. 2 acres zoned R2 Multiple Residence District and 8.45 acres zoned B2 Central Business District. This included single family and multiple dwelling development. North Ridgeville zoning map attached. This valuable and versatile land abuts thriving commercial district on Center Ridge Road and backs up to newer subdivisions and is surrounded by single family homes. Someone can also reap the benefits of simply building 2 additional homes or multi-residential dwellings on the front 2 parcels and not disturb or distract from this private back property with already existing home.  Perfect for developing or find complete seclusion, peace and nature. Property features 2 front lots and middle lot has existing 3,000+ sq ft. single family home that sits far off the road and has its own lake, barn, attached 3 car garage, and large fenced in back yard. Someone can work with this structure or start over. When you visit this property there are so many other amazing features I can share with you. Do not walk the property without setting an appointment. Cameras on property. Proof of funds or pre-approval necessary to view home and agent must be present. Buyer responsible for doing their own due diligence.
